item.title: iPhone and iPod blog
item.description: Some informations for iphone developers, and iphone owners. We have created a new iphone & ipod blog in french, with a dedicated developer category: tout sur l’iphone (everything about the iPhone). I will continue to write iphone development related posts here, mostly traducted from tout sur l’iphone, but if you are a french speaker I recommend you to read the blog first and his developer part which will be bigger.
